subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
organizations: University of Arkansas at Little Rock
lead_paragraph: 11th-seeded Arkansas-Little Rock beat sixth-seeded Texas A&M, 69-60, on Saturday in an opening-round game in the Greensboro Region for Coach Joe Foley’s 700th career victory.
